    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1895-08-12T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1895-08-12T00:00:00-05:00" n="754"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d754">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Andrade</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Olney</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Translation.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Legation of Venezuela</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1895-08-12">
                            <hi rend="italic">August 12, 1895</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Sir</hi>: Referring to the result of the first steps taken
                    by the diplomatic representatives of the United States in France and Belgium,
                    the object of which was to bring about a restoration of harmony between
                    Venezuela and those European States, the minister of foreign relations at
                    Caracas instructs me to convey to your excellency the warmest thanks of the
                    Venezuelan Government for the good offices used in the matter by the United
                    States Government, and to express to you the hope that the aforesaid
                    representatives will avail themselves of any fresh occasion to ventilate the
                    matter under more favorable auspices.</p>
                <p>I avail, etc.,</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">José Andrade.</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
